		<h1>Added to Waiting list: Sorry This Trip is Full.</h1>
		<p>
			| Sorry, this trip is full so you have been added to the trip waiting list. Don't dispair,
			| attendees often cancel opening up slots or, if only a couple people are on the waiting
			| list the trip leader may chooese to force add you or increase the number of maximum
			| attendees. We will notify you if anything changes, please monitor your email for any
			| notices from the trip leader or from the OCVT websytem.
		</p>
